===Etymology===
{{ME.}}, from {{OE.}} ''[[þursdæġ]]'', a contraction of ''[[þunresdæg|þunresdæġ]]'' [[Thor]]’s day, from [[Proto-Germanic]] *''thonaras daga-'', from [[Proto-Indo-European]] *''(s)tene-'', to thunder.

